thread.title: Annalou

author: Annalou
title: Annalou
text:
I am sixty nine, not stupid... writer, artist, performer, illustrator, host for Rap Poetry Jazz Theater gigs, as well as exhibitions of my works. Active in community for ecology and permaculture.
Yet, my computer is running extremely slow because it is not the latest. Built-in faults are rife. I needed assistance, online, with a human. Andrew from Ukraine was patient, clear, very helpful.
I have yet to regain access to my Gmail format. At present it is messed up.
